Chivita is once again at the forefront of providing Nigerians with innovative beverage solutions as it announced the launch of the new Happy Hour Orange Safari flavour. According to the company, the launch is another testament to its continuous drive for product innovation, high quality and sustained consumer satisfaction. Chivita expressed optimism that the new product would drive value and excitement in the flavoured drink segment as it offered yet another appealing product for consumers to choose from. Mrs. Toyin Nnodi, CHI Limited’s Marketing Director, said the launch of Happy Hour Orange Safari was a strategic move for expanding the company’s portfolio of value-added products to meet consumers’ needs. Mrs. Nnodi said, “We are excited to launch Happy Hour Orange Safari; a product we are sure will delight consumers with its natural and refreshing orange taste. Happy Hour Orange Safari delivers on our commitment to provide consumers with more beverage options while staying true to our strong focus of ensuring quality and affordability for all our products.” Consumers happy with ‘Frooty Happy Hour’ new pack Chivita’s Frooty Happy Hour praised by Nigerian consumers Frooty Happy Hour by Chivita receives acclaim from Nigerian consumers